1.title: The Cake Is a Lie!
1.plot: Princess Peach sends a letter to Mario, which is an invitation to come to the castle and have some cake. Mario comes, but there is no cake. Toad reveals that it was a lie because Mario was so fat that Peach wanted to see if Mario would still be able to come through the pipe. Mario rages after he finds Peach and throws her at the castle wall before exploding. Toad then parties because Mario is dead, and Lakitu comments on the footage.
